name: Ayse Banu Tekbas
offering: Business Coaching, Business Consulting, Group Coaching, Mastermind Groups, Online Education for Business Owners
what_you_do: After a long and fast paced corporate ladder climbing, my stress level was beyond normal and slowly my health was detoriating, including my weight – mostly due to stress related binge eating. My main focus in life is enabling people to become themselves and stop seeing themselves from the 'supposed' glasses of others.
who_you_serve: As long as you love yourself, there is always a path to your best and most beautiful and healthy self. This is always a path that a person needs to walk on their own, yet they can also have a guide to highlight the blind spots and hold their hands when needed.
